                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "0ICEJ",
                      "name": "mdH1",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "# 人工智能在医疗领域的突破",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 22,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "uI3Vo",
                      "name": "mdP1",
                      "fill": "#EBEBF5CC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "大家好，欢迎收听本期播客。今天我们来聊一个非常热门的话题——人工智能技术在医疗健康领域的最新突破。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "8cpDG",
                      "name": "mdH2",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "## 影像诊断的革新",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "9B6b1",
                      "name": "mdP2",
                      "fill": "#EBEBF5CC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "首先，我们来看 AI 在医学影像领域的应用。过去医生需要花费大量时间来阅读和分析 CT、MRI 等影像资料，但现在 AI 技术已经可以在几秒钟内完成这些分析工作。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "AzCBC",
                      "name": "mdP3",
                      "fill": "#EBEBF5CC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "根据最新研究数据，AI 辅助诊断在肺结节检测中的准确率已经达到了 97.3%，超过了大部分经验丰富的放射科医生。这不仅提高了诊断效率，更重要的是降低了误诊和漏诊的风险。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "a0340",
                      "name": "mdH3",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "## 药物研发加速",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Obpms",
                      "name": "mdP4",
                      "fill": "#EBEBF5CC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "第二个重要的方向是 AI 在药物研发中的应用。传统的药物研发周期通常需要 10 到 15 年，而 AI 技术正在大幅缩短这个周期…|",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
